31 SUMMARY
3322 This amendment, which is the majority report of the committee, changes the title of
3333 and replaces the resolve and adds an emergency preamble and emergency clause. It also
3344 adds an appropriations and allocations section. The amendment directs the Department of
3355 Economic and Community Development to convene the Blue Economy Task Force to
3366 develop recommendations for the establishment of the Center for the Blue Economy and
3377 to make other recommendations. The task force is directed to submit a report to the Joint
3388 Standing Committee on Housing and Economic Development no later than December 3,
3399 2025, and the committee may report out legislation relating to the report. The amendment
4400 also provides an appropriation of $100,000 in fiscal year 2025-26 to support the Maine
